object_name: Coastal mountain landscape with autumn foliage
background_description: A coastal scene featuring dark blue, rippling ocean water in the foreground, a light brown sandy beach, and a dense forest line displaying a mix of dark green evergreen trees and deciduous trees with yellow and orange autumn foliage. A large, rocky mountain covered in similar varied vegetation rises in the background under an overcast, cloudy sky. Rocky outcrops are visible on the right shore.
explanation: The image depicts a natural landscape consisting of ocean, a beach, a forest, and a mountain under a cloudy sky.
